<p>
<lb n="1"/>kovirācakecari tiripuvanaccak
<lb n="2" break="no"/>karavattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kulottuṅkacoḻa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tevaṟku yāṇṭu Eṭṭāvatu kāṅka
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ya nāṭṭu muttūr veṭkovan kāṇi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yuṭaiya veṭkovan ceviṭai periyā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉu naṭuviṟ periyāṉu ciṟup periyāṉum muttū
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rāḷuṭaiyār kulottuṅkacoḻī<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>ramuṭaiyār taṇ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tecura <hi rend="grantha">śrīhasda</hi>ttāl nāṅkaḷ Ivvaccon<unclear>ṟa</unclear>raiyu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṅ kaikkoṇṭu Ikkoyilukku veṇṭu
</p>

